{id:'sender',title:'Verify the Sender',minutes:5,icon:'bi-person-check',body:'Display names are easy to copy. Inspect the full address and confirm sensitive requests through a trusted, separate channel.'},
{id:'urgency',title:'Resist Urgency and Secrecy',minutes:3,icon:'bi-stopwatch',body:'Attackers manufacture time pressure, fear, and confidentiality. Slow down and follow the normal approval process.'},
{id:'credentials',title:'Protect Credentials and MFA',minutes:5,icon:'bi-shield-lock',body:'Never share passwords or one-time codes. A password manager refusing to fill is a useful warning that the domain is wrong.'},
{id:'mobile',title:'Mobile, QR, and SMS Safety',minutes:4,icon:'bi-phone',body:'Preview QR destinations, avoid shortened SMS links, and use official apps or manually entered websites for payments and account actions.'},
{id:'reporting',title:'Report Quickly',minutes:3,icon:'bi-flag',body:'Report suspicious content using your organization’s process. Fast reporting helps security teams protect everyone else.'},
{id:'access-grants',title:'OTPs, MFA Prompts, and App Permissions',minutes:4,icon:'bi-key',body:'Never read an OTP aloud or type it into another site. Decline unexpected MFA push prompts instead of approving one to silence them, and review what a new app actually requests before granting access.'},
{id:'offline-and-voice',title:'Job Offers, Extensions, and Voice Calls',minutes:4,icon:'bi-mic',body:'Legitimate employers never charge a fee to hire you. Only install browser extensions from official stores after checking the publisher. And remember caller ID can be spoofed and voices can be AI-cloned - verify urgent calls through a separate, known channel before acting.'}
